e":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:24:51.000Z","msg":"成班連登仔又割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9-10 月 掉火魔就係黑警自編自導<br />\n11月 打爆地鐵就係黑警自編自導<br />\n1月 有槍械就係黑警自編自導<br />\n4月 寄粉末信黑警自編自導<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:58:21.000Z","msg":"本身「恐怖分子」呢個label係可以用嚟stigmatize示威者 幫佢哋為打壓唔同意見人士嘅行動建立legitimacy<br />\n例如：<br />\n❌ 警方破獲反送中示威者武器庫<br />\n⭕️ 警方瓦解本土恐怖主義武器庫<br />\n<br />\n而家對家用呢招嚟到搞小動作 之後又有唔少人想同呢個term割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/As0wAWP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAs0wAWP.png&h=02f67898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實比起defend示威者唔係恐怖分子<br />\n冷處理對家嘅論述會唔會好啲<br />\n人哋亂咁鳩噏點解要理佢哋<br />\n你唔係以為反駁/deny呢個label會可以換嚟幾十年嘅太平盛世下話?<br />\n<br />\n學下泰國佬點樣騎劫人哋嘅論述先啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uHjM9h8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHjM9h8.png&h=5bad312f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Meme credit: Nnevvy)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:44:59.000Z","msg":"如果有心人再label對立政見嘅人為「恐怖分子」，應該點騎劫式回應"},{"pid":"f22cb8cad42b7e702c168dc0b5ea4f10e577cb75","tid":1973320,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:47:40.000Z","msg":"白粉報做導演<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e178f6f8e9ebd47c0143d0513bcb8ddae5281842","tid":1973320,"uid":70898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:48:06.000Z","msg":"想扮有人寄咩？ <br />\n想屈人係恐怖分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932104d0849130eb6502fb3e33122e7e1ac7cbad","tid":1973320,"uid":186181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"搞咁耐忠誠勇毅